text: Clifton Freeman Cash (born 1980 in Gastonia, North Carolina) is an American stand-up comedian from North Carolina, United States. ==Personal life== Clifton Freeman Cash was born in 1980, He has a brother named Wiley Cash and they grew in Gastonia, North Carolina. == Comedy Special == Cliff Cash released a comedy special called The Long Road in 2024. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:American stand-up comedians
title: Cliff Cash
